### EC-OPS — Agent Endpoints
### AG-UI SSE stream and A2A protocol
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Note: SSE responses stream line-by-line — REST Client shows them as they arrive
###
### Authentication: get a token from auth.http first, then paste it below.
### For the SSE stream you may also pass the token as ?token=<jwt> if your
### client cannot set a custom header on EventSource.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8002
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ── AG-UI SSE stream ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Each response is a stream of newline-delimited SSE events:
###   data: {"type":"RunStarted", ...}
###   data: {"type":"TextDelta", "delta":"..."}
###   data: {"type":"ToolCallStart", "tool_name":"..."}
###   data: {"type":"ToolCallResult", "result":{...}}
###   data: {"type":"UiAction", "action":"order_card", "payload":{...}}
###   data: {"type":"RunFinished"}

### Create an order via natural language
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=Create%20an%20order%20for%20David%20with%202%20notebooks%20at%20%248.50%20each%20and%201%20pen%20at%20%241.25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List all current orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=List%20all%20orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List only pending orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=Show%20me%20all%20pending%20orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get a specific order by ID — paste real ID
@agentOrderId = REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=Get%20order%20{{agentOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Cancel an order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=Cancel%20order%20{{agentOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Complex — create then describe
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/stream?message=Create%20an%20order%20for%20Emma%20with%203%20items%3A%20a%20laptop%20stand%20for%20%2445%2C%20a%20webcam%20for%20%2279.99%2C%20and%20an%20LED%20desk%20lamp%20for%20%2332.50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ── A2A Agent Card ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Discover agent capabilities
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/agent.json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ── A2A Task submission ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Submit a task — returns 202 immediately with a task ID
# @name a2aTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/a2a/tasks/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "Create an order for Frank with 1 standing desk at $349.00"
}

###

### Poll task status — paste task ID from response above
@taskId = REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/a2a/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Poll — list orders via A2A
# @name a2aListTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/a2a/tasks/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "List all orders with status PENDING"
}

###

### Get non-existent task → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/a2a/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
